@michaelllam and I threw together these elopement plans so quickly. Initially, for us to celebrate in a way that was more true to us, but looking back it feels like the only way a Mike + Nic wedding could have gone. So many little mishaps along the way, but so much joy and laughter and memories shared with our dearest friends and family. Maybe someday we’ll put together a more traditional celebration for those who were not able to attend the elopement, but for now…this was the most beautiful way I could have imagined beginning life with my bebby. Thank you so much to @samanthaloganphotography and @cristianherreramiguel for capturing the day. Thank you to our friends who pitched in throughout the weekend and kept the ship from sinking! Thank you @jovojovojovo for making the most incredible wedding cakes we could have ever asked for. Thank you to our best friends @_sunkyungee @hnsnth for planning with and supporting us the whole weekend. Just so many thanks to be given for the life we’re allowed to build rn.
